  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat oven to 350°F (180°C).",
    "2. Toss walnuts with a pinch of salt and spread on a baking sheet.",
    "3. Bake for 5-7 minutes, or until caramelized.",
    "4. In a large bowl, combine mixed greens, crumbled feta, and chopped parsley.",
    "5. In a small bowl, whisk together balsamic vinaigrette and a pinch of salt.",
    "6. Drizzle dressing over salad and toss to coat.",
    "7. Top with caramelized walnuts and dried cranberries.",
    "8. Sprinkle pecorino cheese over salad and serve."
